$interpreted: Ru-yi: Sophie, we're sleeping in the same room...
Minnie: *groan*...
Sophie: Are you okay?
Minnie: I'm fine. Feels like there's pressure in my chest. If I lie down for a bit, I'll be just fine.
Sophie: Let me take you to the room to rest.
Sophie: Sorry, everybody. I've got to help my mom...she's got to rest. Feel free to head to your rooms.
Hutchinson: Sophie, don't worry about us. Miss Minnie's health is the most important.
Ru-yi: Hanbei, I get what you're saying.
Hanbei: Minnie always used to use this to get attention.
Hutchinson: Huh? What are you saying?
Ru-yi: Hutchinson is too much of a gentleman. He wouldn't understand.
Hutchinson: Although I don't quite understand, I thank you for the compliments.
Hanbei: Wait a second, looks like we're one person short.
Ru-yi: Rune!?
Sophie: You rest for a bit. I'll come for you a little later.
Minnie: Soph, I haven't seen you for so long. How about you sleep in this room?
Rune: I don't want to.
Sophie: Rune!? How'd you get here?
Rune: Rune and Sophie...sleep together.
Minnie: Do you two...normally sleep in the same room?
Sophie: What? No, no, no, no!
Sophie: How do I say...Rune is like a little child. He doesn't understand how the world works. He sort of clings to people...
Minnie: I understand.
Sophie: Rune, go find Hanbei and them. I'll see you when we eat.
Rune: Rune listens...to Sophie.
Minnie: If only I had found you years earlier. It must have been so hard on you for all these years.
Sophie: Momma...
Minnie: You're finally ready to call me mom.
Minnie: Little Soph, stay with me forever, won't you? I don't want to lose you ever again...
Sophie: I...
Hanbei: While we were eating, every time I wanted to talk to Sophie, Minnie kept interrupting me with her "headaches".
Ru-yi: Now that I think about it, I hardly had a chance to speak with Sophie today.
Hutchinson: It's probably because Minnie hasn't spoken with Sophie in such a long time. Hanbei, don't be jealous.
Rune: Rune...likes jelly.
Ru-yi: Oh, not like that. Hanbei also wants to spend time with Sophie. He's just jealous~
Rune: Oh...Rune is...jealous.
Hutchinson: You all shouldn't be upset. We should be happy for Sophie.
Ru-yi: A thief! He's burning Sophie's luggage!
Rune: No! That's Sophie's!
Sophie: What happened?
Rune: A thief just grabbed Sophie's luggage.
Sophie: What!? No way!
Rune: Don't...run!!
Sophie: Where do you think you are going?
Hanbei: Sophie, Ru-yi was a little bit frightened by all this. Why don't you take her to her room to rest?
Ru-yi: Huh? I wasn't scared at all!
Ru-yi: Oh...I mean, whaaaaa! Scared me half to death. Sophie, please, won't you accompany me to my room~~
Sophie: Ehh~ Okay~
Hutchinson: Hanbei, are you thinking what I'm thinking?
Hanbei: I hope we're just overthinking things...
